to watch them all the time.

1422
01:07:51,632 --> 01:07:54,113
He let me used to
watch to time the laps.

1423
01:07:54,157 --> 01:07:56,159
But didn't your dad
always argue with your mom

1424
01:07:56,202 --> 01:07:57,377
all that time?

1425
01:07:57,421 --> 01:07:59,597
Yes, now she fights
with us instead.

1426
01:07:59,640 --> 01:08:03,992
I kind of miss him.

1427
01:08:04,036 --> 01:08:05,864
I got to go.

1428
01:08:17,180 --> 01:08:18,659
Excuse me.

1429
01:08:18,703 --> 01:08:22,663
Karen, listen, you can't
let your parents split up.

1430
01:08:22,707 --> 01:08:23,708
We got to do something.

1431
01:08:23,751 --> 01:08:25,536
Well, what are we going to do?

1432
01:08:25,579 --> 01:08:27,886
I'll think of something.

1433
01:08:27,929 --> 01:08:30,845
KAREN: No, you goof, my mom
wouldn't call him Mr. Roberts.

1434
01:08:30,889 --> 01:08:33,631
JAMES: Oh, yeah, so what
do they call each other

1435
01:08:33,674 --> 01:08:37,461
when they're, you know, mushy?

1436
01:08:37,504 --> 01:08:38,723
I don't know, pookey.

1437
01:08:43,119 --> 01:08:50,474
Pookey, I don't want to fight.

1438
01:08:50,517 --> 01:08:54,304
Meet me at Case Luna at 6:00.

1439
01:08:54,347 --> 01:08:56,262
Oh, good.

1440
01:08:56,306 --> 01:08:58,134
I know Mrs. Roberts
is in the meeting,

1441
01:08:58,177 --> 01:09:01,180
but can I leave a
message from her husband?

1442
01:09:01,224 --> 01:09:03,269
Meet him at Case Luna at 6:00.

1443
01:09:03,313 --> 01:09:04,314
Thank you.

1444
01:09:04,357 --> 01:09:06,446
Oh, and don't worry about Karen.

1445
01:09:06,490 --> 01:09:07,708
She has a sitter.

1446
01:09:07,752 --> 01:09:08,622
Bye.

1447
01:09:08,666 --> 01:09:09,928
Thank you.

1448
01:09:09,971 --> 01:09:11,843
A sitter.

1449
01:09:11,886 --> 01:09:14,715
[music playing]

1450
01:09:20,721 --> 01:09:23,420
[singing in spanish]

1451
01:09:39,175 --> 01:09:40,001
Two, please.

1452
01:09:50,273 --> 01:09:52,057
MR ROBERTS: Hi, honey.

1453
01:09:52,100 --> 01:09:52,971
Hi.

1454
01:09:53,014 --> 01:09:54,364
Oh, they kissed.

1455
01:09:54,407 --> 01:09:55,234
Oh, romantic.

1456
01:09:58,281 --> 01:09:59,456
God, this place.

1457
01:09:59,499 --> 01:10:00,892
A lot of memories for us.

1458
01:10:00,935 --> 01:10:02,285
Oh, yeah, there are.

1459
01:10:02,328 --> 01:10:04,461
I'm just glad you came
to your senses, Estelle.

1460
01:10:04,504 --> 01:10:05,375
That's cute.

1461
01:10:05,418 --> 01:10:08,116
My senses.

1462
01:10:08,160 --> 01:10:09,901
Well, you invited me here.

1463
01:10:09,944 --> 01:10:11,119
And--

1464
01:10:11,163 --> 01:10:12,382
What are you talking about?

1465
01:10:12,425 --> 01:10:14,688
You sent me a little note.

1466
01:10:14,732 --> 01:10:16,124
What note?

1467
01:10:16,168 --> 01:10:18,257
Kenneth, if this is
some kind of joke,

1468
01:10:18,301 --> 01:10:19,954
I don't think it's very funny.

1469
01:10:19,998 --> 01:10:21,782
You called me Pookey.

1470
01:10:21,826 --> 01:10:23,436
Pookey.

1471
01:10:23,480 --> 01:10:24,916
Believe me, there's a lot of
things I'd like to call you.

1472
01:10:24,959 --> 01:10:28,572
And Pookey is not one of them.

1473
01:10:28,615 --> 01:10:30,313
Forget it, let's just go home.

1474
01:10:30,356 --> 01:10:31,923
Oh, mayday, mayday.

1475
01:10:31,966 --> 01:10:34,708
I didn't like
this place anyway.

1476
01:10:34,752 --> 01:10:36,057
Look, it's coach.

1477
01:10:39,583 --> 01:10:40,497
Hi, cousin.

1478
01:10:40,540 --> 01:10:41,715
What a coincidence.

1479
01:10:41,759 --> 01:10:43,021
Isn't this funny?

1480
01:10:43,064 --> 01:10:44,022
Yeah.

1481
01:10:44,065 --> 01:10:45,241
Would you like to join us?

1482
01:10:45,284 --> 01:10:46,111
No.

1483
01:10:46,154 --> 01:10:47,025
No.

1484
01:10:47,068 --> 01:10:48,635
We were just going.

1485
01:10:48,679 --> 01:10:50,115
We're absolutely stuffed.

1486
01:10:50,158 --> 01:10:50,942
Have you ordered yet?

1487
01:10:54,772 --> 01:10:55,903
See you later.

1488
01:10:58,993 --> 01:11:01,169
[school bell ringing]

1489
01:11:01,213 --> 01:11:02,910
This is it, test day.

1490
01:11:02,954 --> 01:11:03,868
Clear your desks.

1491
01:11:14,313 --> 01:11:15,401
Where's Sam?

1492
01:11:15,445 --> 01:11:16,359
Does anyone know?

1493
01:11:16,402 --> 01:11:18,622
Is he sick today?

1494
01:11:18,665 --> 01:11:21,494
[music playing]

1495
01:11:33,854 --> 01:11:35,203
Oh, little bird.

1496
01:11:38,816 --> 01:11:40,992
You folks leave you?

1497
01:11:41,035 --> 01:11:42,341
Well, you don't need them.

1498
01:11:49,261 --> 01:11:50,044
OK, begin.

1499
01:11:56,007 --> 01:11:59,315
