1500
01:11:59,358 --> 01:12:02,187
Mr. Roberts,
these are the Banks.

1501
01:12:02,230 --> 01:12:03,493
That's Sam's mom and dad.

1502
01:12:06,670 --> 01:12:09,934
You're right.

1503
01:12:09,977 --> 01:12:11,370
Let me ask the kids.

1504
01:12:11,414 --> 01:12:12,545
Just a minute.

1505
01:12:12,589 --> 01:12:14,199
All right, stop working.

1506
01:12:14,242 --> 01:12:16,027
This is very important.

1507
01:12:16,070 --> 01:12:19,160
Sam has not been
home since yesterday.

1508
01:12:19,204 --> 01:12:22,250
If any of you know where
he is you have to tell me.

1509
01:12:22,294 --> 01:12:24,383
I promise he won't be punished.

1510
01:12:24,427 --> 01:12:26,864
You understand this
is very serious.

1511
01:12:26,907 --> 01:12:28,431
We're all concerned
for Sam's safety.

1512
01:12:32,652 --> 01:12:35,525
This is our fault.
We got him into this

1513
01:12:35,568 --> 01:12:37,178
because of the stupid war.

1514
01:12:37,222 --> 01:12:39,398
Sam did what he
wanted to do, James.

1515
01:12:39,442 --> 01:12:41,400
We didn't do anything.

1516
01:12:41,444 --> 01:12:43,054
I knew something was
wrong with him yesterday.

1517
01:12:43,097 --> 01:12:44,142
I've got to find him.

1518
01:12:44,185 --> 01:12:45,012
What?

1519
01:12:45,056 --> 01:12:47,145
Are you crazy?

1520
01:12:47,188 --> 01:12:50,017
James, wait.

1521
01:12:50,061 --> 01:12:52,280
OK, everybody everything's OK.

1522
01:12:52,324 --> 01:12:55,240
Mr. Roberts, he's going
to help look for Sam.

1523
01:12:55,283 --> 01:12:57,416
And I'm going to help him by
watching you take your test.

1524
01:12:57,460 --> 01:12:58,635
So all eyes on your papers.

1525
01:12:58,678 --> 01:12:59,549
Let's go.

1526
01:12:59,592 --> 01:13:01,942
Do your best.

1527
01:13:01,986 --> 01:13:05,337
[music playing]

1528
01:13:25,313 --> 01:13:27,228
Look at the ball.

1529
01:13:27,272 --> 01:13:29,274
Anticipate my move.

1530
01:13:29,317 --> 01:13:31,015
Yes, very good.

1531
01:13:31,058 --> 01:13:31,885
There's a problem.

1532
01:13:31,929 --> 01:13:32,799
