Go on in.

1535
01:13:35,628 --> 01:13:36,977
- His folks say--
- Good work.

1536
01:13:37,021 --> 01:13:38,370
He didn't come
home last night.

1537
01:13:38,414 --> 01:13:39,676
Did they call police?

1538
01:13:39,719 --> 01:13:40,981
Oh, yeah they've
been out all morning.

1539
01:13:41,025 --> 01:13:41,895
I should've known
there was a problem.

1540
01:13:41,939 --> 01:13:42,940
You would have.

1541
01:13:42,983 --> 01:13:44,420
You give me too much credit.

1542
01:13:44,463 --> 01:13:45,856
I'm a soccer coach.

1543
01:13:45,899 --> 01:13:47,814
I can't read their minds.

1544
01:13:47,858 --> 01:13:49,642
Help me out here.

1545
01:13:49,686 --> 01:13:51,601
Sam's parents just split up.

1546
01:13:51,644 --> 01:13:53,559
I think he took it pretty hard.

1547
01:13:53,603 --> 01:13:56,910
Now, you're a kid, you're
angry at the world.

1548
01:13:56,954 --> 01:13:57,911
What would you do?

1549
01:13:57,955 --> 01:13:59,304
What about that clubhouse?

1550
01:13:59,347 --> 01:14:00,479
Huh?

1551
01:14:00,523 --> 01:14:02,525
They didn't check
the clubhouse?

1552
01:14:02,568 --> 01:14:03,917
What clubhouse?

1553
01:14:03,961 --> 01:14:05,223
Let's go.

1554
01:14:05,266 --> 01:14:08,095
[music playing]

1555
01:14:20,847 --> 01:14:22,806
JAMES: Sam?

1556
01:14:22,849 --> 01:14:24,329
Sam, are you here?

1557
01:14:31,292 --> 01:14:32,642
Where'd you go?

1558
01:14:53,489 --> 01:14:56,361
[music playing]

1559
01:15:31,875 --> 01:15:33,224
Please hurry.
What if he's hurt?

1560
01:15:33,267 --> 01:15:34,094
Don't worry.

1561
01:15:34,138 --> 01:15:35,095
Sam's a good kid.

1562
01:15:35,139 --> 01:15:37,924
He won't do anything stupid.

1563
01:15:37,968 --> 01:15:40,797
[music playing]

1564
01:16:02,296 --> 01:16:03,341
Sam.

1565
01:16:03,384 --> 01:16:04,124
Sam.

1566
01:16:08,259 --> 01:16:09,477
Where's the famous clubhouse?

1567
01:16:09,521 --> 01:16:11,871
It's got to be
around here somewhere.

1568
01:16:11,915 --> 01:16:12,872
Sam.

1569
01:16:12,916 --> 01:16:13,786
Sam.

1570
01:16:13,830 --> 01:16:14,874
Sam.

1571
01:16:14,918 --> 01:16:18,269
[music playing]

1572
01:16:40,770 --> 01:16:43,947
