1573
01:16:43,990 --> 01:16:45,644
Hi, James.

1574
01:16:45,688 --> 01:16:48,081
Wouldn't it be
cool to fly, James?

1575
01:16:48,125 --> 01:16:50,083
I dreamt about it.

1576
01:16:50,127 --> 01:16:52,216
My mom and dad were down
there yelling at me.

1577
01:16:52,259 --> 01:16:53,913
And then they got smaller
and smaller till they

1578
01:16:53,957 --> 01:16:55,306
