1579
01:16:55,349 --> 01:16:56,873
Yeah, that's cool all right.

1580
01:16:56,916 --> 01:16:58,614
But that's just in dreams.

1581
01:16:58,657 --> 01:16:59,484
I know.

1582
01:17:20,461 --> 01:17:21,549
You see that?

1583
01:17:21,593 --> 01:17:22,681
Yeah.

1584
01:17:22,725 --> 01:17:24,422
Come on.

1585
01:17:24,465 --> 01:17:27,338
[music playing]

1586
01:17:40,830 --> 01:17:42,483
I left my jacket
in the clubhouse.

1587
01:17:42,527 --> 01:17:43,310
Let's go get it.

1588
01:17:46,705 --> 01:17:47,488
Over here.

1589
01:17:56,628 --> 01:17:57,673
MR ROBERTS: I got him.

1590
01:18:00,763 --> 01:18:04,592
Sam, oh, Sam, oh, baby.

1591
01:18:04,636 --> 01:18:05,376
Sam.

1592
01:18:08,509 --> 01:18:11,425
I'm glad you're back.

1593
01:18:11,469 --> 01:18:13,819
I don't want to let you go.

1594
01:18:33,360 --> 01:18:36,189
[knocking]

1595
01:18:59,691 --> 01:19:02,041
[splashing]

1596
01:19:03,695 --> 01:19:04,652
The fish!

1597
01:19:04,696 --> 01:19:07,612
The fish!

1598
01:19:07,655 --> 01:19:10,528
[yelling]

1599
01:19:17,013 --> 01:19:18,492
I got him.

1600
01:19:18,536 --> 01:19:19,885
I got him.

1601
01:19:26,979 --> 01:19:30,417
Give him a pencil.

1602
01:19:30,461 --> 01:19:32,332
Get him a test.

1603
01:19:35,031 --> 01:19:38,382
All right, everybody,
emergency is over.

1604
01:19:38,425 --> 01:19:40,123
The fish is fine.

1605
01:19:40,166 --> 01:19:41,646
See.

1606
01:19:41,689 --> 01:19:42,473
Get back to work.

1607
01:19:45,389 --> 01:19:48,305
Did somebody move?

1608
01:19:48,348 --> 01:19:50,481
No, ma'am.

1609
01:19:50,524 --> 01:19:51,308
OK.

1610
01:20:01,274 --> 01:20:04,277
Kids, you'll be happy to
know that Sam has been found.

1611
01:20:04,321 --> 01:20:05,539
And he's back with
his mom and dad.

1612
01:20:05,583 --> 01:20:06,323
He's fine.

1613
01:20:08,673 --> 01:20:10,196
Don't be so modest, Ken.

1614
01:20:10,240 --> 01:20:12,372
Your class should know.

1615
01:20:12,416 --> 01:20:15,158
Mr. Roberts is the
one who found Sam.

1616
01:20:23,383 --> 01:20:24,602
All right, now let's
get back to work.

1617
01:20:29,650 --> 01:20:31,348
OK, time's up.

1618
01:20:31,391 --> 01:20:33,045
Pass your tests forward.

1619
01:20:37,310 --> 01:20:38,834
I'm dead.

1620
01:20:38,877 --> 01:20:40,313
You didn't get
to do any of it?

1621
01:20:40,357 --> 01:20:41,880
I didn't even hand it in.

1622
01:20:41,924 --> 01:20:43,055
I don't think he'll
give us points

1623
01:20:43,099 --> 01:20:43,926
